  "page": "Artos the Strong",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\">Artos the Strong</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Artos the Strong</b> is one of the many legendary heroes of the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>, whose tales date back to the <a href=\"/index.php/Age_of_Heroes\" title=\"Age of Heroes\">Age of Heroes</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>It is unknown if Artos is related to <a href=\"/index.php/House_Strong\" title=\"House Strong\">House Strong</a>, a family from the riverlands with <a href=\"/index.php/First_Men\" title=\"First Men\">First Men</a> origin.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Artos_the_Strong&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Riverlands.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403131220\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.081 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.325 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 393/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10354/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3064/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 316/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 567/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.230/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.48 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  320.110      1 -total\n 98.01%  313.740      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 97.48%  312.048      1 Template:Infobox\n 12.70%   40.667     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.25%   10.404      2 Template:Infobox_label\n  1.54%    4.921      1 Template:Ref\n  0.96%    3.083      1 Template:Ref/core\n  0.40%    1.284      1 Template:References\n  0.39%    1.256      2 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:18861-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403131220 and revision id 298022\n -->\n",
